properties.title: Reclaimed Wood from Deconstructed Homes to Framing by Urban Ashes
properties.description: Reclaim Detroit’s primary focus is to divert as much material from Detroit’s 78,000 vacant structures from landfills as possible and will do so by using a process called Deconstruction.
Handmade from reclaimed wood in Detroit, Michigan, The Reframe offers a beautiful and easy way to elevate any 5x7” card into art.
